---
title: Tuscan Beef Linguine with Sweet Bell Peppers and Parmesan
description: Juicy ground beef and garlic create a savoury flavour base for this classic pasta sauce. Enhanced with sweet peppers, chili and Parmesan cheese, this recipe is so simple and delicious, you'll want it to become a part of your weekly repertoire.
